# Frontend brand patches (baked bundles + assets).
# Populated by `scripts/apply-patches.sh` from the official release tarball.
# Not committed: the JS bundles are compiled artefacts without source maps.
# We must NOT use `patches/` (directory ignore) here, because that would
# also block the .gitkeep placeholders. Instead, list the specific files
# that apply-patches.sh writes.
/patches/index.html
/patches/favicon.png
/patches/favicon.svg
/patches/sxdevops-ai-agent-promo.html
/patches/urls.py
/patches/assets/*.js
/patches/assets/*.html
/patches/assets/*.css
/patches/assets/*.map

